<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENBP70A0000006" svcinfotypenbr = "01" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Warning for Wheel (with Tire) Removal
</title>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
A wheel may fall off the axle and cause an injury if all of the wheel bolts are removed at the same time.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
When removing the last wheel bolt, be sure to hold the wheel so that it does not fall off the axle.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
